# Projocalypse file and directory naming

Adapted from [talemail](https://github.com/alienfacepalm/talemail) conventions: **kebab-case** for all TypeScript module paths on disk. React component **symbols** in code stay **PascalCase**.

Related: **`projocalypse-typescript.mdc`** (symbols inside files).

## Source (`src/**`)

| Location | File pattern | Example |
|----------|--------------|---------|
| `src/components/**` (layout, project, task, my-tasks, `ui/`) | **kebab-case** `.tsx` | `task-detail-panel.tsx`, `board-view.tsx`, `button.tsx` |
| `src/hooks/`, `src/lib/`, `src/db/`, `src/context/` | **kebab-case** `.ts` / `.tsx` | `use-project-view-mode.ts`, `export-import.ts`, `task-drag.ts` |
| `src/models/` | **kebab-case** `.ts` for modules; legacy `types.ts` unchanged | `types.ts` (legacy) |
| `src/styles/` | **kebab-case** `.css` | `globals.css` |

- **Directories** under `src/` use **kebab-case** (`my-tasks/`, `project/`, `task/`).
- **Symbols in code** stay conventional: React components and types remain **PascalCase**; functions and variables use **camelCase**. Only **paths on disk** follow this rule.

### Toolchain entry files (keep as-is)

Bundler or framework entry files the toolchain expects by name may keep that name:

- `src/App.tsx`, `src/main.tsx`
- `index.html`, `vite.config.ts`, `eslint.config.js`

Prefer kebab-case for everything else you add under `src/`.

### Legacy (no rename unless the task includes migration)

- `src/models/types.ts` — keep filename; migrate symbols per **`projocalypse-typescript.mdc`**

## Cursor rules and skills (`.cursor/`)

| Kind | Pattern | Example |
|------|---------|---------|
| Project rules | `projocalypse-<topic>.mdc` | `projocalypse-typescript.mdc` |
| Project skills | `projocalypse-<topic>/` directory | `projocalypse-pr-loop/` |
| Skill `name` in frontmatter | `projocalypse-<topic>` | `projocalypse-karpathy-guidelines` |

Lowercase, kebab-case, short and specific — not `projocalypse-stuff`.

## Documentation

| Location | Pattern | Example |
|----------|---------|---------|
| Repo root | `README.md` | `README.md` |
| Future `doc/` tree (if added) | **CAPITALIZED** directory and **UPPER-KEBAB** or **UPPERCASE** filenames | `doc/PLAN/ROADMAP.md` |

Matches talemail `talemail-docs.mdc` doc layout; Projocalypse has no `doc/` tree yet — apply when one is added.

## Export / backup filenames

- JSON backups: `projocalypse-backup-YYYY-MM-DD.json` (kebab-case, lowercase product slug).

## When editing

- **New files** must follow the table above.
- **Renames** only when the task explicitly includes migration — avoid drive-by renames.
